  "body": "### Component\n\nCast\n\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\n\n- [X] Foundry\n- [X] Foundryup\n\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\n\nforge 0.2.0 (b192af4 2022-05-30T00:04:26.5131178Z)\n\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\n\ncast --to-wei\n\n### Operating System\n\n_No response_\n\n### Describe the bug\n\nSometimes `cast --to-wei` introduces a rounding error. For example, `cast --to-wei 2.3` returns 2299999999999999700. I am guessing this is an upstream bug with `ethers_core::utils::parse_units`.",
